The python package we need to install:
-requests
-BeautifulSoup(or beautifulsoup4)
-lxml
-pandas
-matplotlib

The scrape.py is used for requesting data form weather.com/tenday/l/...,that is 10 days label page on the website.
Then it will creat a .cvs profile named 'Future Weather' to storage responesed data.

The polt.py is used for showing the Higest/Lowest temperature in 2 future weeks.
